name: Limited Edition- The 206 Dice Tee
description:
The Dice Tee- Here for a limited time,

Show your inner nerd with the new 206 -D6 dice tee. This new Tee from handsIn Apparel, features three D6 that read "2 0 6" in reference to Seattle's main area code. With one of the biggest gamer communities out there, Seattle is the perfect hub for nerds like us. Roll the dice on this one and snag a tee before they are gone!

These tees are American Apparel (Color: Grass) 100% Fine Jersey Cotton unisex tees. The softest, smoothest, best-looking short sleeve tee shirt available anywhere! For exact color and sizing guide, check out: http://store.americanapparel.net/2001.html

name: Pride of Washington -The Wazzu Tee
description:
Show your pride for Washington State University with this brand new tee from HandsIn Apparel. These shirts are Athletic Gray with crimson vintage fade print and are In stock now!

Part of a Limited Release first edition Line- 
These new shirts feature custom woven tags that are hand sewn by us on to the tee giving priority attention to premium quality. The shirts are printed with a vintage fade ink. These are super soft unisex Canvas 3001 Fashion Fit preshrunk high end 100% cotton tees. Since they are fitted, some folks like to order one size larger than normal, the choice is yours. All shirts we designed and created here in Washington.

Sizing chart available on FAQ link on our home page. If you would like to request another size or color for our next order, please use the HandsIn Apparel contact form at the bottom of the page! Enjoy!

*Allow 7-10 days for delivery since the labels are hand sewn on, in house, and shipping can take a bit.

Any sizes that sell out can be requested for re-order abe@handsinforgoodtimes.com
